    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cacio e pepe sauce with fresh tagliatelle </strong>and drizzle over your <strong>truffle oil</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
